    <center><h1>String Utilities</h1></center>

    <hr>
    <a name="StringUtil"></a>
    <h2>class StringUtil</h2>

    <h3>#include "StringUtil.h"</h3>

    The StringUtil class provides static methods for:
    <ul>
    <li>determining if one string is a prefix of another string
    <li>determining if one string is a suffix of another string
	<li>converting a string to lower-case
	<li>trimming the whitespace from the beginning and ending of a string
    </ul>

    <h3>Methods</h3>

    <h3>static bool IsPrefix(const string & str, const string & prefix)</h3>
    Returns true if prefix is a prefix of str, and false if it is not.

    <h3>static bool IsSuffix(const string & str, const string & suffix)</h3>
    Returns true if suffix is a suffix of str, and false if it is not.

    <h3>static void ToLower(string & str)</h3>
	Converts each character in str to lower-case.

	<h3>static void Trim(string & str)</h3>
	Removes all leading and trailing whitespace from str.

